                  <name type="place" key="Clearwater (Flathead, Kooskooskee) River">koos keich keich</name>
               </hi> means "clear water." Josephy (NP), 5; Space, 8. Or it may represent the <name type="native_nation" key="Nez Perce Indians">Nez Perce</name> term <hi rend="italic">qu·sqú·s,</hi> "blue gray."</note>
